name: Cyberpunk Samurai
description:
RKF S4M - Sam is a "Rise Kill First" unit Samurai dispatched to kill zombie cyborgs. 
The concept started last year in an observation to see what themes would make an interesting character for 2020's digital art scene. 
I really enjoyed working on this one, took its time but I managed to use 3D and sculpting to get the details I needed. 
Hope you like her <3
